Setup a destination service class with a dedicated repack-destination tape-pool:

Identify your disk servers:

-bash-3.2$ stager_qry -s | grep DiskServer
  DiskServer lxc2disk07.cern.ch DISKSERVER_PRODUCTION   CAPACITY 160945766400 FREE 80105460( 0%)
  DiskServer lxc2disk08.cern.ch DISKSERVER_PRODUCTION   CAPACITY 160945766400 FREE 152853708680(94%)
-bash-3.2$

Logon to each disk server and stop the rfiod daemon:

-bash-3.2$ ssh root@lxc2disk07.cern.ch
[root@lxc2disk07 ~]# /etc/init.d/rfiod stop
[root@lxc2disk07 ~]# exit
-bash-3.2$ ssh root@lxc2disk08.cern.ch
[root@lxc2disk08 ~]# /etc/init.d/rfiod stop
[root@lxc2disk08 ~]# exit

Repack a tape:

